Contact Us

Helping industry leading specialty businesses grow

Contact Us

While our expertise and programs are firmly grounded in today’s challenges, we aim to redefine specialty insurance by creatively leveraging data and analytics to develop sophisticated, customer-centric programs.

FUTURE PROOF

Built for Today and Tomorrow

To be relevant in today’s environment and meet the challenges of the future, you need to stay a step ahead. 

Specialty Program Group delivers leading-edge specialty expertise backed by transformative digital capabilities and sophisticated data and analytics. 

This unique approach helps us better serve our customers and carrier partners today and meet their needs in the future.

OUR APPROACH

Scale For An Entrepreneurial Spirit

Our goal is to partner with industry-leading specialty businesses to provide them with the ability to achieve their goals and optimize their businesses. 

Specialty Program Group offers access to capital and investment, deep carrier relationships, creative thinking, product development and broad distribution, while allowing our businesses to maintain the essence of what makes them successful.

OUR COMMITMENT

Business Growth

Specialty Program Group offers a unique platform for growth, reach and efficiency to boutique specialty program, wholesale, and retail businesses, and we enable the delivery of valuable, innovative and differentiated solutions to their customers.

    A PERFECT MATCH

    What We Look For In A Partner

    Industry-Leading

    We look for businesses that are already successful at their specialty. We’re not looking for businesses that need to be rescued.

    Leadership

    We are looking for leaders and teams that will make us better as much as we are committed to do the same for them.

    Culture

    People are everything to us. We have created a great culture and we’ll continue to have a strict no-assh*le policy.
